## Navigation Patterns

- **Root**: [src/navigation/index.tsx](mdc:src/navigation/index.tsx) defines `HomeTabs` and `RootStack` via `createStaticNavigation`
- **Screens**
  - Tabs: `ChatList`, `About` with header button to `Settings`
  - Stack: `Chat`, `Profile` (deep link), `Settings` (modal), `NotFound`
- **Deep linking**
  - Scheme: `chatdns://` (see [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) and [app.json](mdc:app.json))
  - `Profile` path: `:user(@[a-zA-Z0-9-_]+)` with parse/stringify
- **Adding a screen**
  - Add component under `src/navigation/screens/*`
  - Register it inside the `screens` map in `HomeTabs` or `RootStack`
  - Provide `options` in place; keep titles concise; avoid side-effects in options
- **Icons**
  - Use [src/components/InfoIcon.tsx](mdc:src/components/InfoIcon.tsx) and [src/components/icons/SettingsIcon.tsx](mdc:src/components/icons/SettingsIcon.tsx)
- **Do not**
  - Instantiate navigators outside `src/navigation/index.tsx`
  - Bypass the static navigation pattern